room_title: Escape room "V.I.P.E.R's Nest" by Break Through Sac in Sacramento
room_address: 1338 Howe Ave, Building B Suite 200, Sacramento, CA 95825
room_description:
Extortion. Bribery. Murder. These are just a few of the crimes you attribute to a shadowy criminal organization known only as V.I.P.E.R. And yet, you've been stonewalled at every step of the investigation. You've been told to let it go... but you must bring them down.
With no one to trust, you and your team will have to go rogue, defying orders and putting it all on the line. You have to infiltrate the VIP lounge in the casino V.I.P.E.R uses to launder its funds. Cut off the head of the snake before you get caught. Failure will mean life in prison... or worse.
